					<p>
						I recently finished my PhD in <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/">Bren School of Information &amp; Computer Sciences</a> 
						at<a href="http://www.uci.edu/"> UCI</a> and joined <a href = "www.bing.com">Microsoft Bing</a>.
						I worked with <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Elopes/">Prof. Lopes</a> during my PhD. My  <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~sjavanma/thesis.pdf"> thesis </a> was about measuring content quality in user generated content systems using machine learning. <br><br>	
                                           My resume in PDF can be found <a href="Sara-Javanmardi-Resume.pdf">here</a> (updated Dec. 2012). </p>
					
					
                                   
