												<a href="http://research.microsoft.com/en-us/groups/isrc/">Internet Services Research Center</a>  
											</b>
											<br>
											On improving search results rankings using 2-stage smoothing bigram language models. The goal was 
											to find a ranking algorithm with higher accuracy in terms of NDCG values compared to BM25. <a href="file:///C:/Documents%20and%20Settings/sjavanma.UCI-ICS/My%20Documents/Downloads/MSR-Report.pdf">Technical Report</a> 
										</td>
